  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/71174574/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u71174574-3.jpg" class="pil" alt="Estrella" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/71174574/">Estrella</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
      <br/>


          <span class="">不一样的咪蒙，有才华有见地，而不是只会发泄情绪的怨妇。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
